## Cross-System Context

### Integration Points

| System | Integration |
|--------|-------------|
| Claude Code | Skills extend Claude's capabilities |
| PAI | Similar skill system - potential alignment |
| web-terminal-frontend-tests | Could use screenshot skill |

### Quality Workflow

```
Work Session N
      │
      ▼
┌─────────────┐
│ telemetry-  │
│   judge     │
└─────┬───────┘
      │
      ├── PASS → Output advances
      ├── REVISE → Session N+1 gets feedback
      └── REJECT → Must reformulate approach
```

### Ralph Loop Integration

For iterative refinement with quality gates:

```bash
/ralph-loop "Write X. Use /judge to evaluate. Output <promise>PASS</promise> when Judge returns PASS." --completion-promise "PASS" --max-iterations 5
```

## Configuration

### Installation Location

Skills symlinked to `~/.claude/skills/`

### SKILL.md Frontmatter

```yaml
---
name: skill-name           # Required
description: ...           # Required - includes USE WHEN triggers
version: 1.0.0            # Optional
---
```

